0labeled%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BTrump%20Elections%20Team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-election-integrity-trey-trainor-federal-election-commission-fec-2022-6%5C%22%3EInsider%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Trainor%2C%20who%20was%20previously%20appointed%20to%20the%20commission%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20was%20billed%20as%20a%20member%20of%20Trump's%20team%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20by%20the%20Denton%20County%20Republican%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20report%2C%20the%20FEC's%20Office%20of%20the%20Inspector%20General%20began%20an%20investigation%20into%20Trainor's%20perceived%20ethical%20impropriety.%20They%20that%20while%20it%20may%20appear%20he%20acted%20improperly%2C%20his%20billing%20was%20written%20without%20his%20knowledge%2C%20undermining%20%26quot%3Bany%20appearance%20of%20impropriety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Trainor%20did%20speak%20to%20Insider%20in%202022%20for%20comment%2C%20the%20FEC%20Office%20of%20the%20Inspector%20General's%20report%20notes%20that%20he%20and%20his%20counsel%20refused%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20government's%20investigation%2C%20leading%20to%20%26quot%3Buncertainty%26quot%3B%20regarding%20the%20investigation's%20final%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20Commissioner%20Trainor%20nor%20his%20counsel%20responded%20to%20numerous%20attempts%20over%20the%20course%20of%20several%20months%20by%20the%20OIG%20to%20schedule%20an%20interview%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%20%26quot%3BHis%20lack%20of%20participation%20impeded%20the%20OIG's%20efforts%20to%20gather%20relevant%20evidence%20and%20resulted%20in%20uncertainty%20concerning%20the%20conclusions%20in%20this%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20from%20the%20FEC%20Office%20of%20the%20Inspector%20General%20notes%20that%20Trainor's%20lack%20of%20cooperation%20with%20the%20investigation%20ran%20counter%20to%20guidance%20from%20f