olitics-for-5-years%2Farticleshow%2F102546821.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-poll-panel-disqualifies-imran-from-electoral-politics-for-5-years%2Famp_articleshow%2F102546821.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-poll-panel-disqualifies-imran-from-electoral-politics-for-5-years%2Famp_articleshow%2F102546821.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sharad%20Pawar's%20Big%20Claim%20On%20Vijaya%20Raje%20Scindia's%20'Babri%20Assurance'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20movement%20gathered%20steam%20in%201992%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Vijaya%20Raje%20Scindia%20had%20assured%20then%20prime%20minister%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20that%20nothing%20would%20happen%20to%20Babri%20Masjid%20and%20he%20believed%20her%20against%20the%20advice%20of%20his%20ministers%2C%20NCP%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%20revealed%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20launch%20of%20senior%20journalist%20Neerja%20Chowdhury's%20book%20'How%20Prime%20Ministers%20Decide'%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%2C%20who%20was%20the%20defence%20minister%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%2C%20said%20he%20along%20with%20then%20home%20minister%20and%20the%20home%20secretary%20was%20present%20at%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20group%20of%20ministers%20and%20I%20was%20one%20of%20them...%20It%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20should%20call%20a%20meeting%20of%20leaders%20of%20the%20respective%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NCP%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20that%20meeting%2C%20Vijaya%20Raje%20Scindia%20had%20assured%20the%20prime%20minister%20that%20nothing%20would%20happen%20to%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%20that%20while%20he%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20and%20home%20secretary%20felt%20anything%20could%20happen%2C%20Rao%20chose%20to%20believe%20Scindia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Chowdhury%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20recalled%20a%20conversation%20that%20Rao%20had%20with%20some%20senior%20journalists%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20mosque%20demolition%20where%20the%20prime%20minister%20was%20asked%20what%20he%20was%20doing%20when%20the%20demolition%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claimed%20that%20Rao%20had%20told%20journalists%20that%20he%20allowed%20it%20to%20happen%20because%20it%20would%20end%20a%20festering%20sore%20and%20he%20felt%20the%20BJP%20would%20lose%20its%20main%20political%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20was%20launched%20by%20Mr%20Pawar%2C%20along%20with%20Kerala%20Governor%20Arif%20Mohammad%20Khan%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Shashi%20Tharoor%2C%20former%20railway%20minister%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Dinesh%20Trivedi%2C%20and%20Maharashtra's%20former%20CM%20Prithviraj%20Chavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discussion%20was%20moderated%20by%20senior%20journalist%20Rajdeep%20Sardesai.%20Trivedi%20recalled%20the%20time%20of%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20as%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20role%20of%20Arun%20Nehru%2C%20one%20of%20his%20key%20advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArun%20Nehru%20was%20like%20family...%20That%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20periods%20and%20if%20it%20continued%20things%20would%20be%20very%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Trivedi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrithviraj%20Chavan%2C%20who%20served%20as%20a%20Union%20minister%20in%20the%20UPA%20government%2C%20said%20not%20handling%20the%20Anna%20Hazare%20movement%20properly%20caused%20the%20downfall%20of%20the%20Congress-led%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20caused%20that%20downfall%20was%20what%20happened%20immediately%20before%20that.%20Scams%2C%202G...%20We%20didn't%20handle%20Anna%20Hazare%20rightly.%20That's%20what%20brought%20an%20end%20to%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20former%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20was%20good%20at%20b