soldiers%20worked%20on%20methods%20to%20disguise%20their%20command%20posts%20and%20move%20them%20quickly%20if%20found%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExamples%20from%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%20have%20shown%20that%20large%20and%20static%20footprints%20can%20be%20targeted%20and%20destroyed%20within%20minutes%20of%20enemy%20fires%20unmasking%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Australian%20army%20Col.%20Benjamin%20McLennan%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Australia%20army%20command%20post%20Talisman%20Sabre%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d065f420f1cf0019cba6cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Australian%20army%20HX77%20truck%20moves%20command-post%20components%20into%20place%20during%20Talisman%20Sabre%20on%20July%2021.%3Cp%3EAustralian%20army%2FCpl.%20Nicole%20Dorrett%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECommand%20posts%20are%20nodes%20for%20military%20officers%2C%20intelligence%20and%20communications%20specialists%2C%20and%20other%20troops%20directing%20battlefield%20operations.%20They%20are%20usually%20packed%20with%20electronic%20equipment%20and%20surrounded%20by%20vehicles%2C%20giving%20them%20a%20distinct%20electronic%20and%20physical%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20see%20a%20number%20of%20radio%20stations%20in%20the%20same%20place%2C%20I%20understand%20it's%20a%20command%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20Col.%20Ivan%20Pavlenko%2C%20chief%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20General%20Staff's%20electronic%20and%20cyber%20warfare%20department%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66279650%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20BBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proliferation%20of%20intelligence-gathering%20assets%20and%20of%20precision%20guided%20weapons%20has%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20find%20the%20distinctive%20pre