e%20US%20Air%20Force%20said%20it%20found%20unsafe%20levels%20of%20possible%20cancer-causing%20chemicals%20at%20a%20Montana%20base.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20found%20the%20chemicals%20in%20nuclear%20missile%20launch%20control%20centers%20at%20Malmstrom%20Air%20Force%20Base.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20military%20previously%20decided%20to%20investigate%20unusual%20blood%20cancer%20cases%20among%20missileers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Air%20Force%20revealed%20this%20week%20that%20it%20found%20unsafe%20levels%20of%20probable%20cancer-causing%20chemicals%20in%20nuclear%20missile%20launch%20control%20centers%20at%20a%20base%20in%20Montana.%20The%20discovery%20comes%20after%20the%20US%20military%20decided%20to%20investigate%20unusual%20blood%20cancer%20cases%20among%20several%20military%20officers%20who%20had%20worked%20at%20the%20site.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20experts%20that%20carried%20out%20testing%20at%20Malmstrom%20Air%20Force%20Base%20in%20June%20discovered%20levels%20of%20polychlorinated%20biphenyls%20(PCBs)%20that%20were%20above%20federally%20recommended%20thresholds%20in%20two%20facilities%20at%20the%20site%2C%20Air%20Force%20Global%20Strike%20Command%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Fpcbs%2Flearn-about-polychlorinated-biphenyls%5C%22%3EPCBs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bgroup%20of%20man-made%20organic%20chemicals%26quot%3B%20that%20it%20considers%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bprobable%20human%20carcinogens%26quot%3B%20and%20have%20a%20demonstrated%20ability%20to%20cause%20a%20range%20of%20negative%20health%20effects%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20for%20PCBs%20and%20other%20potential%20contaminants%2C%20the%20experts%20collected%20300%20surface%20swipe%20samples%20across%20Malmstrom's%20launch%20control%20centers%2C%20which%20is%20where%20individuals%20can%20control%20and%20monitor%20missile%20launch%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20the%20swipes%2C%20279%20returned%20non-detectable%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Air%20Force%20said.%20%26quot%3BOf%20the%2021%20with%20detectable%20results%2C%2019%20were%20below%20the%20mitigation%20level%20established%20by%20federal%20law%20and%20regulation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20air%20samples%20of%20the%20launch%20control%20centers%20and%20launch%20control%20support%20building%20revealed%20any%20detectable%20levels%20for%20PCBs.%20They%20only%20appeared%20in%20the%20surface%20swipes.%20It%20is%20unclear%20how%20many%20individuals%20may%20have%20been%20exposed%20to%20these%20likely%20carcinogens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20initial%20results%20from%20the%20survey%20team%2C%20which%20discovered%20PCB%20levels%20above%20the%20cleanup%20threshold%20designated%20by%20law%20in%20two%20of%20our%20facilities%2C%20I%20directed%20Twentieth%20Air%20Force%20to%20take%20immediate%20measures%20to%20begin%20the%20cleanup%20process%20for%20the%20affected%20facilities%20and%20mitigate%20exposure%20by%20our%20Airmen%20and%20Guardians%20to%20potentially%20hazardous%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gen.%20Thomas%20Bussiere%2C%20commander%20of%20Air%20Force%20Global%20Strike%20Command%2C%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20measures%20will%20stay%20in%20place%20until%20I%20am%20satisfied%20that%20we%20are%20providing%20our%20missile%20community%20with%20a%20safe%20and%20clean%20work%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22FILE%20-%20In%20this%20image%20provided%20by%20the%20U.S.%20Air%20Force%2C%20Airman%201st%20Class%20Jackson%20Ligon%2C%20left%2C%20and%20Senior%20Airman%20Jonathan%20Marinaccio%2C%20341st%20Missile%20Maintenance%20Squadron%20technicians%20connect%20a%20re-entry%20system%20to%20a%20spacer%20on%20an%20intercontinental%20ballistic%20missile%20during%20a%20Simulated%20Electronic%20Launch-Mi