ll%20replace%20the%20Rules%20of%20Procedure%20and%20Conduct%20of%20Business%20of%20UP%20Legislative%20Assembly%2C%201958.%20%26quot%3BThe%20new%20rule%20was%20tabled%20on%20Monday.%20Discussion%20on%20it%20will%20take%20place%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20subsequently%20it%20will%20be%20passed%2C%26quot%3B%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20Speaker%20Satish%20Mahana%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20set%20of%20rules%2C%20MLAs%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20tear%20any%20document%20in%20the%20House.%20They%20will%20also%20not%20point%20towards%20anyone%20in%20the%20gallery%20while%20delivering%20a%20speech%20or%20praise%20him%2Fher.%20The%20legislators%20will%20neither%20be%20able%20to%20stand%20nor%20sit%20with%20their%20backs%20towards%20the%20Speaker.%20They%20will%20also%20not%20be%20able%20to%20bring%20or%20display%20weapons%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20members%20cannot%20smoke%20nor%20can%20they%20talk%20or%20laugh%20loudly%20in%20the%20lobby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rules%20state%20that%20the%20members%20of%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20(MLAs)%20should%20show%20respect%20by%20bowing%20towards%20the%20Speaker's%20chair%2C%20and%20not%20show%20their%20backs%20while%20entering%20or%20leaving%20the%20House%20or%20while%20sitting%20or%20rising%20from%20their%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20the%20duration%20for%20summoning%20a%20session%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%20has%20been%20halved%20to%20seven%20days%20from%20the%2014%20days%20at%20present.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20the%20members%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20any%20literature%2C%20questionnaire%2C%20book%20or%20press%20comments%20inside%20or%20distribute%20slips%20not%20related%20to%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20behalf%20of%20the%20principal%20secretary%20of%20the%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20a%20list%20of%20work%20of%20each%20day%20will%20have%20to%20be%20made%20available%20to%20the%20MLAs%20online%20or%20offline.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20on%20December%206%20last%2C%20SP%20MLA%20Atul%20Pradhan%20was%20caught%20live%20streaming%20proceedings%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20on%20Facebook%20Live%20while%20holding%20a%20protest%20in%20the%20well%20over%20the%20Rampur%20bypolls%2C%20drawing%20the%20ire%20of%20the%20Speaker%20who%20asked%20him%20to%20leave%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20has%20a%20403-member%20legislative%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691515620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-09%2Fjlgg035o_up-assembly_625x300_19_September_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-rules-of-up-assembly-no-mobile-phones-tearing-of-documents-laughing-out-loud-4280659%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Legislative%20Assembly%20is%20all%20set%20to%20pass%20a%20new%20set%20of%20rules%20under%20which%20members%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20take%20their%20mobile%20phones%20inside%20the%20House%2C%20tear%20documents%20or%20stand%20or%20sit%20with%20their%20backs%20towards%20the%20Speaker.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-rules-of-up-assembly-no-mobile-phones-tearing-of-documents-laughing-out-loud-4280659%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-rules-of-up-assembly-no-mobile-phones-tearing-of-documents-laughing-out-loud-4280659%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-rules-of-up-assembly-no-mobile-phones-tearing-of-documents-laughing-out-loud-4280659%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20shares%20excitement%20about%20Hollywood%20debut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22pub