n%20the%20Moon's%20surface%20on%20August%2023%20even%20if%20all%20the%20sensors%20and%20two%20of%20its%20engines%20do%20not%20work%2C%20ISRO%20chairman%20S%20Somanath%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20design%20of%20the%20lander%20%E2%80%98Vikram'%20has%20been%20made%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20makes%20sure%20that%20it%20would%20be%20able%20to%20handle%20failures%2C%20Mr%20Somanath%20said%20during%20a%20talk%20on%20%E2%80%98Chandrayaan-3%3A%20Bharat's%20Pride%20Space%20Mission'%2C%20hosted%20by%20the%20non-profit%20organisation%20Disha%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20everything%20fails%2C%20if%20all%20the%20sensors%20fail%2C%20nothing%20works%2C%20still%20it%20(Vikram)%20will%20make%20a%20landing.%20That's%20how%20it%20has%20been%20designed%20--%20provided%20that%20the%20propulsion%20system%20works%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Somanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20blasted%20into%20Space%20on%20July%2014%20and%20it%20entered%20into%20lunar%20orbit%20on%20August%205.%20There%20will%20be%20three%20more%20de-orbiting%20manoeuvres%20--%20exercises%20to%20bring%20it%20closer%20to%20the%20Moon%20so%20that%20Vikram%20lands%20on%20the%20Moon's%20surface%20on%20August%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20de-orbiting%20manoeuvres%20will%20be%20performed%20on%20August%209%2C%20August%2014%2C%20and%20August%2016%20till%20its%20orbit%20reduces%20to%20100%20kmx100%20km%20from%20the%20Moon%2C%20Mr%20Somanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lander%20propulsion%20module%20separation%20exercise%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20subsequently%2C%20soon%20after%20lander%20%26quot%3Bdeboost%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20process%20that%20slows%20down%20the%20craft.%20It%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20landing%20on%20lunar%20surface%20on%20August%2023%2C%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20also%20made%20sure%20that%20if%20two%20of%20the%20engines%20(in%20Vikram)%20don't%20work%20this%20time%20also%2C%20it%20will%20still%20be%20able%20to%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ISRO%20chairman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20the%20whole%20design%20has%20been%20made%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20it%20(Vikram)%20should%20be%20able%20to%20handle%20many%20failures%2C%20provided%20the%20algorithms%20work%20properly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20challenge%20before%20the%20ISRO%20team%2C%20according%20to%20him%2C%20is%20to%20make%20a%20horizontal%20%E2%80%98Vikram'%20land%20vertically%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Somanath%20said%20once%20the%20lander%20separates%20from%20the%20orbiter%2C%20it%20will%20move%20horizontally.%20Through%20a%20series%20of%20manoeuvres%2C%20it%20will%20be%20brought%20to%20a%20vertical%20stance%20in%20order%20to%20land%20safely%20on%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20exercise%20is%20crucial%2C%20as%20ISRO%20failed%20to%20get%20its%20lander%20to%20touchdown%20safely%20on%20the%20Moon's%20surface%20during%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20ability%20to%20transfer%20from%20horizontal%20to%20vertical%20direction%20is%20the%20trick%20we%20have%20to%20play%20here.%20Here%20only%20we%20had%20the%20problem%20last%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Somanath%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20is%20also%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20fuel%20consumed%20is%20lesser%2C%20the%20distance%20calculations%20are%20correct%20and%20all%20the%20algorithms%20work%20properly%2C%20the%20ISRO%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20ISRO%20team%20this%20time%20has%20made%20arrangements%20to%20ensure%20that%20Vikram%20makes%20an%20attempt%20to%20land%20property%20even%20if%20there%20are%20some%20variations%20in%20the%20calculations%2C%20Mr%20Somanath%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20the%20lander%20will%20have%20four%20payloads%3A%20Chandra's%20Surface%20Thermo%20Physical%20Experiment%20(ChaSTE)%20will%20carry%20out%20the%20measurements%20of%20thermal%20properties%20of%20lunar%20surface%20near%20polar%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERAMBHA-LP%20payload%20will%20measure%20the%20near%20surface%20plasma%20(ions%20and%20electrons)%20density%20and%20its%20changes%20with%20time%3B%20Laser%20Retroreflector%20Array%20from%20NASA%20for%20accurate%20positioning%20measurement%20of%20the%20lander%20on%20lunar%20surface%20by%20future%20orbiters%3B%20and%20Instrument%20for%20Lunar%20Seismic%20Activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rover%20named%20%E2%80%98Pragyan'%20will%20have%20three%20payloads%3A%20The%20Laser%20Induced%20Breakdown%20Spectroscope%20(LIBS)%20will%20determine%20the%20elemental%20composition%20of%20lunar%20soil%20and%20rocks%20around%20the%20lunar%20landing%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Alpha%20Particle%20X-Ray%20Spectrometer%20(APXS)%20payload%20will%20derive%20the%20chemical%20composition%20and%20infer%20mineralogical%20composition%20to%20further%20enhance%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpectro-polarimetry%20of%20Habitable%20Planet%20Earth%20(SHAPE)%20is%20an%20experimental%20payload%20in%20Pragyan%20to%20study%20the%20spectro-polarimetric%20signature%20of%20the%20habitable%20planet%20Earth%20in%20the%20near-infrared%20(NIR)%20wavelength%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691513340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Frotit2lc_chandrayaan-3-launch_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-plans-proper-touchdown-of-vikram-lander-even-if-its-sensors-and-engines-fail-isro-chief-s-somanath-4281013%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vikram%2C%20the%20lander%20of%20India's%20third%20lunar%20mission%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20will%20be%20able%20to%20make%20a%20soft-landing%20on%20the%20Moon's%20surface%20on%20August%2023%20even%20if%20all%20the%20