0when%20there%20is%20a%20genuine%20constitutional%20issue%26quot%3B.%20But%20even%20there%2C%20the%20interpretation%20of%20the%20constitution%20is%20%26quot%3Bdynamic%26quot%3B%20and%20changes%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bmindset%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20court%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20note%20of%20criticism%20towards%20the%20earlier%20governments%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bleft%20important%20decisions%20to%20courts%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20of%20the%20day%20maintains%20a%20line%20of%20distinction%20between%20courts%2C%20and%20government...%20and%20is%20making%20policies%20proactively%2C%26quot%3B%20Harish%20Salve%20said%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20NDTV's%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%20as%20part%20of%20a%20special%20series%20to%20mark%20the%2076th%20Independence%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20example%2C%20he%20cited%20the%20situation%20when%20kar%20sevaks%20were%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%201992.%20Whether%20the%20army%20should%20take%20action%20on%20not%20was%20not%20a%20decision%20the%20government%20was%20willing%20to%20take%2C%20and%20they%20had%20left%20it%20to%20courts.%20There%20on%2C%20every%20decision%20of%20import%20was%20left%20to%20courts%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20downside%20of%20it%20became%20clear%20in%20the%20coal%20scam%20case%2C%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20cancelled%20mining%20licenses.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20lost%20face%20globally%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20word%20of%20warning%20--%20%26quot%3BA%20court%20must%20reconsider%20its%20position%20as%20governments%20are%20now%20experimenting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Salve%20--%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sought-after%20veteran%20lawyers%20in%20India%20---%20also%20enumerated%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20legal%20system%2C%20remarking%20that%20the%20courts%20have%20gone%20from%20being%20%26quot%3Bleftist%20to%20centrist%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20%26quot%3Bexpanded%20its%20jurisdiction%20to%20social%20issues%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20also%20is%20a%20fallout%20of%20the%20people's%20approach.%20%26quot%3BCourts%20must%20not%20be%20first-stop%20shop%20for%20every%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20courts%20also%20%26quot%3Bmust%20intervene%20only%20when%20there%20is%20a%20genuine%20constitutional%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Black%20of%20trust%26quot%3B%20in%20India's%20litigation%20processes%20globally%2C%20said%20Mr%20Salve%2C%20who%20has%20represented%20the%20country%20in%20crucial%20cases%20in%20the%20international%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20can%20become%20arbitration%20centre%20only%20when%20we%20develop%20confidence%20in%20Indian%20courts%E2%80%A6%20India%20must%20evolve%20better%20litigation%2C%20dispute%20resolution%2C%20arbitration%20processes%26quot%3B.%20India%2C%20he%20added%2C%20can%20only%20become%20an%20arbitration%20centre%20if%20%26quot%3Bregressive%20mindsets%26quot%3B%20can%20be%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20wide-ranging%20interview%2C%20Mr%20Salve%20said%20the%20perception%20about%20India%20has%20changed%20abroad%2C%20bringing%20about%20a%20%26quot%3B180-degree%20turn%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20world%20is%20turning%20to%20India%20for%20business%2C%20investment%20prospects%20and%20India%20is%20being%20looked%20at%20as%20economic%20powerhouse%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Salve%20said%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bquantum%20change%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnAsked%20about%20the%20key%20forward-looking%20steps%20the%20country%20should%20take%2C%20Mr%20Salve%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20vision%20is%20to%20transform%20India%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20political%20powerhouse%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BPM%20Modi's%20grand%20reception%20in%20foreign%20countries%20is%20a%20first%20for%20any%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%A6%20The%20role%20India%20playing%20in%20global%20disputes%20like%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20is%20remarkable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20government's%20global%20mindset%20is%20missing%20in%20other%20institutions%20and%20services%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20focus%20on%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20is%20getting%20%26quot%3Bbogged%20down%26quot%3B%20by%20states.%20%26quot%3BIndians%20should%20trust%20their%20economy%E2%80%A6%20Indians%20must%20become%20aspirational%20as%20our%20economy%20progresses%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691512620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fj5s6bbn_hairsh-salve-ndtv-interview_625x300_08_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjudges-appointing-judges-a-deeply-flawed-system-harish-salve-4281148%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Harish%20Salve%2C%20the%20former%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%2C%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20judicial%20appointments%20issue%20today%2C%20saying%20judges%20appointing%20judges%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20flawed%20system%26quot%3B%20that%20doesn't%20exist%20anywhere%20else%20in%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjudges-appointing-judges-a-deeply-flawed-system-harish-salve-4281148%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjudges-appointing-judges-a-deeply-flawed-system-harish-salve-4281148%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjudges-appointing-judges-a-deeply-flawed-system-harish-salve-4281148%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tesla's%20Shock%20Shakeup%20Renews%20Uncertainty%20Over%20Leadership%20Succession%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETesla%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%20Zachary%20Kirkhorn%20stepped%20down%20after%2013%20years%20at%20the%20electric-vehicle%20maker%2C%20a%20surprise%20shakeup%20that%20raises%20new%20questions%20about%20succession%20in%20the%20top%20ranks%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirkhorn%2C%20one%20of%20just%20four%20executive%20officers%20and%20a%20prominent%20voice%20for%20the%20company%20with%20shareholders%2C%20resigned%20from%20his%20duties%20August%204%2C%20the%20company%20said%20Monday%20in%20a%20regulatory%20filing.%20He'll%20continue%20to%20serve%20in%20an%20unspecified%20capacity%20through%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20%26quot%3Bto%20support%20a%20seamless%20transition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Accounting%20Officer%20Vaibhav%20Taneja%20took%20on%20the%20CFO%20role%20in%20addition%20to%20his%20current%20duties%2C%20Tesla%20said.%20Taneja%2C%2045%2C%20held%20several%20positions%20at%20the%20EV%20maker%20before%20becoming%20accounting%20chief%20in%202019.%20He%20previously%20worked%20at%20PricewaterhouseCoopers%20in%20India%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20shares%20fell%201%25%20in%20New%20York.%20The%20stock%20price%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20so%20far%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirkhorn's%20departure%20comes%20as%20Tesla%20builds%20a%20new%20factory%20in%20Mexico%20and%20prepares%20to%20bring%20its%20Cybertruck%20pickup%20to%20market%20as%20it%20fends%20off%20rivals%20in%20the%20increasingly%20crowded%20EV%20market.%20Tesla%20has%20lowered%20prices%20across%20its%20lineup%20to%20maintain%20its%20position%20atop%20the%20electric-car%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20done%20a%2013-year%20tour%20of%20duty%20working%20for%20Elon%2C%20which%20is%20like%20working%2050%20years%20for%20anyone%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gene%20Munster%2C%20managing%20partner%20of%20Deepwater%20Asset%20Management.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20he's%20sticking%20around%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20bodes%20well%20for%20the%20transition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20departure%20of%20Kirkhorn%2C%20who%20was%20considered%20a%20top%20contender%20to%20succeed%20Musk%20as%20chief%20executive%20officer%2C%20renews%20uncertainty%20over%20leadership%20at%20Tesla.%20It%20also%20instantly%20raises%20the%20profile%20of%20Taneja%2C%20who%20wasn't%20among%20the%2016%20executives%20invited%20on%20stage%20with%20Musk%20at%20an%20investor%20meeting%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20thanked%20Kirkhorn%20in%20a%20tweet%20and%20acknowledged%20that%20his%20tenure%20wasn't%20an%20easy%20one.%20He%20didn't%20give%20any%20hints%20about%20what%20might%20be%20next%20for%20the%20outgoing%20executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20Zach%20Kirkhorn%20for%20his%20many%20contributions%20to%20Tesla%20over%20the%20course%20of%2013%20often%20difficult%20years.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMuch%20appreciated%20and%20best%20wishes%20for%20the%20next%20stage%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1688662299857321984%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirkhorn%20joined%20Tesla%20in%202010%20as%20a%20senior%20financial%20analyst%20and%20was%20promoted%20five%20times%2C%20most%20recently%20to%20CFO%20in%20early%202019%20at%20the%20age%20of%2034.%20Before%20he%20took%20over%2C%20Tesla%20had%20a%20long%20history%20of%20losses%20and%20occasionally%20burned%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20of%20cash%20per%20quarter.%20The%20company%20has%20been%20consistently%20profitable%20since%20then%20and%20repaid%20about%20%2410%20billion%20of%20debt%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20helping%20it%20secure%20investment-grade%20ratings.%20It%20also%20joined%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20Index%20in%20December%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirkhorn%2C%20a%20graduate%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20worked%20under%20his%20predecessors%20as%20CFO%2C%20Deepak%20Ahuja%20and%20Jason%20Wheeler.%20He%20spoke%20at%20length%20on%20Tesla's%20quarterly%20earnings%20calls%20and%20was%20well-regarded%20by%20investors%20for%20reining%20in%20costs.%20He%20regularly%20talked%20about%20how%20recurring%20revenue%20from%20software%20would%20play%20an%20increasing%20role%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZach%20did%20a%20great%20job%20expanding%20margins%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Munster.%20%26quot%3BUsually%20when%20companies%20scale%20up%20production%2C%20their%20margins%20come%20under%20pressure.%20He%20threaded%20the%20needle%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20hard%20thing%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirkhorn%20owned%20197%2C540%20shares%20as%20of%20last%20month%2C%20according%20to%20data%20compiled%20by%20Bloomberg%2C%20a%20holding%20valued%20at%20about%20%2449%20million.%20He%20recently%20sold%20about%20%241%20million%20of%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20a%20part%20of%20this%20company%20is%20a%20special%20experience%20and%20I'm%20extremely%20proud%20of%20the%20work%20we've%20done%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirkhorn%20wrote%20Monday%20on%20LinkedIn.%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20want%20to%20thank%20Elon%20for%20his%20leadership%20and%20optimism%2C%20which%20has%20inspired%20so%20many%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirkhorn%20was%20a%20calm%2C%20steady%20presence%20on%20earnings%20calls%2C%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20Musk's%20infamous%20bombast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArk%20Investment%20Management%20CEO%20%26amp%3B%20Chief%20Investment%20Officer%20Cathie%20Wood%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Bloomberg%20Television%20on%20Monday%20that%20she%20will%20miss%20Kirkhorn's%20presence%20but%20that%20Taneja%20is%20well-suited%20to%20take%20on%20the%20CFO%20job.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20miss%20him%20but%20his%20successor%20has%20been%20at%20Tesla%20right%20underneath%20him%20since%202018%2C%26quot%3B%20Wood%20said%20of%20Kirkhorn%20and%20Taneja.%20%26quot%3BHe%20trained%20his%20successor%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20the%20largest%20individual%20contributor%20to%20Ark's%20flagship%20Ark%20Innovation%20ETF.%20It%20accounts%20for%20almost%2011%25%20of%20the%20net%20asset%20value%20of%20the%20fund%2C%20according%20to%20data%20compiled%20by%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%20added%20%26quot%3BMaster%20of%20Coin%26quot%3B%20to%20his%20job%20title%20in%20early%202021%2C%20about%20a%20month%20after%20Tesla%20disclosed%20it%20had%20made%20a%20%241.5%20billion%20investment%20in%20Bitcoin.%20The%20tongue-in-cheek%20title%20was%20given%20at%20the%20same%20time%20Musk%20became%20%26quot%3BTechnoking%20of%20Tesla.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20filing%20Monday%20did%20not%20mention%20%26quot%3BMaster%20of%20Coin%26quot%3B%20as%20one%20of%20Taneja's%20roles%20as%20new%20CFO.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691512500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-01%2Fa584l4ag_tesla-generic_625x300_09_January_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-elon-musks-master-of-coin-steps-down-focus-on-tesla-succession-4281004%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%20Zachary%20Kirkhorn%20stepped%20down%20after%2013%20years%20at%20the%20electric-vehicle%20maker%2C%20a%20surprise%20shakeup%20that%20raises%20new%20questions%20about%20succession%20in%20the%20top%20ranks%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20company.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-elon-musks-master-of-coin-steps-down-focus-on-tesla-succession-4281004%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-elon-musks-master-of-coin-steps-down-focus-on-tesla-succession-4281004%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-elon-musks-master-of-coin-steps-down-focus-on-tesla-succession-4281004%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bollywood%20actor