bby-deol-nobody-was-willing-to-join-hands-with-us%2Farticleshow%2F102544245.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Once%20We%20Cease%20To%20Be%20Judges...%5C%22%3A%20Chief%20Justice%20On%20Ranjan%20Gogoi's%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20on%20Tuesday%20remarked%20that%20once%20judges%20demit%20office%20whatever%20they%20say%20is%20just%20opinion%20and%20is%20not%20binding%2C%20after%20former%20CJI%20Ranjan%20Gogoi's%20comments%20that%20the%20basic%20structure%20doctrine%20was%20debatable%20was%20flagged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Justice%20(retd)%20Gogoi%2C%20now%20a%20nominated%20member%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20while%20participating%20in%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20book%20by%20(TR)%20Andhyarujina%2C%20the%20former%20solicitor%20general%2C%20on%20the%20Kesavananda%20Bharati%20case.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BHaving%20read%20the%20book%2C%20my%20view%20is%20that%20the%20doctrine%20of%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution%20has%20a%20very%20debatable%20jurisprudential%20basis.%20I%20would%20not%20say%20anything%20more%20than%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20landmark%20Kesavananda%20Bharati%20verdict%20of%201973%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20propounded%20the%20basic%20structure%20doctrine%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20held%20that%20certain%20fundamental%20features%20such%20as%20democracy%2C%20secularism%2C%20federalism%20and%20rule%20of%20law%20cannot%20be%20amended%20by%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20appearing%20for%20National%20Conference%20leader%20Mohd%20Akbar%20Lone%20who%20has%20challenged%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Constitution%20which%20had%20accorded%20special%20status%20to%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20referred%20to%20Justice%20Gogoi's%20statement%20made%20in%20the%20Upper%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20Sibal%20contended%20that%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20Centre%20abrogated%20the%20special%20status%20of%20J%20and%20K%20cannot%20be%20in%20any%20way%20justified%20%26quot%3Bunless%20a%20new%20jurisprudence%20is%20brought%20so%20that%20they%20(Centre)%20can%20do%20whatever%20they%20like%20as%20long%20as%20they%20have%20a%20majority%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bnow%20one%20of%20your%20esteemed%20colleagues%20has%20said%20that%20in%20fact%20basic%20structure%20theory%20is%20also%20doubtful%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Mr%20Sibal's%20submission%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMr%20Sibal%2C%20when%20you%20refer%20to%20a%20colleague%2C%20you%20have%20to%20refer%20to%20a%20sitting%20colleague.%20Once%20we%20cease%20to%20be%20judges%2C%20whatever%20we%20say%2C%20they%20are%20just%20opinions%20and%20are%20not%20binding.%26quot%3B%20It%20may%20be%20recalled%20that%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20had%20at%20a%20public%20event%20in%20January%20this%20year%20had%20called%20the%20basic%20structure%20doctrine%20a%20'North%20Star'%20that%20guides%20and%20gives%20certain%20direction%20to%20the%20interpreters%20and%20implementers%20of%20the%20Constitution%20when%20the%20path%20ahead%20is%20convoluted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20basic%20structure%20principle%20became%20the%20ground%20for%20setting%20aside%20several%20Constitutional%20amendments%2C%20including%20the%20quashing%20of%20the%20amendment%20and%20the%20corresponding%20NJAC%20Act%20on%20the%20appointment%20of%20judges%20in%20the%20higher%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20who%20is%20appearing%20for%20the%20Centre%20in%20the%20Article%20370%20case%2C%20intervened%20when%20Mr%20Sibal%20made%20the%20submission%20and%20said%20proceedings%20in%20Parliament%20cannot%20be%20discussed%20before%20the%20court%20just%20like%20the%20court's%20proceedings%20are%20not%20discussed%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Sibal%20is%20addressing%20here%2C%20since%20he%20wasn't%20there%20in%20Parliament%20yesterday.%20He%20should%20have%20responded%20in%20the%20Parliament.%26quot%3B%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20who%20is%20an%20independent%20MP%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20agreed%20with%20Tushar%20Mehta's%20submission%20and%20said%20he%20was%20not%20in%20Parliament%20on%20Monday%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20GNCTD%20amendment%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20the%20Nani%20A%20Palkhivala%20Memorial%20Lecture%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20January%2021%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20had%20said%20craftsmanship%20of%20a%20judge%20lies%20in%20interpreting%20the%20text%20of%20the%20Constitution%20with%20the%20changing%20times%20while%20keeping%20its%20soul%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20basic%20structure%20of%20our%20Constitution%2C%20like%20the%20North%20Star%2C%20guides%20and%20gives%20certain%20direction%20to%20the%20interpreters%20and%20implementers%20of%20the%20Constitution%20when%20the%20path%20ahead%20is%20convoluted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20basic%20structure%20or%20the%20philosophy%20of%20our%20Constitution%20is%20premised%20on%20the%20supremacy%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20separation%20of%20powers%2C%20judicial%20review%2C%20secularism%2C%20federalism%2C%20freedom%20and%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20individual%20and%20the%20unity%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20nation.%26quot%3B%20The%20remarks%20by%20the%20CJI%20came%20days%20after%20Vice%20President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20had%20questioned%20the%20Kesavananda%20Bharati%20case%20verdict%20and%20said%20he%20does%20not%20subscribe%20to%20its%20conclusion%20that%20Parliament%20can%20amend%20the%20Constitution%20but%20not%20its%20basic%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVice%20President%20Dhankhar%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%2C%20had%20said%20the%20verdict%20set%20a%20bad%20precedent%20and%20if%20any%20authority%20questions%20Parliament's%20power%20to%20amend%20the%20Constitution%2C%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20say%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20a%20democratic%20nation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20asserted%20that%20parliamentary%20sovereignty%20and%20autonomy%20are%20quintessential%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20democracy%20and%20cannot%20be%20permitted%20to%20be%20compromised%20by%20the%20executive%20or%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%2083rd%20All%20India%20Presiding%20Officers%20Conference%20in%20Jaipur%20on%20January%2011%2C%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said%20the%20judiciary%20cannot%20intervene%20in%20lawmaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%201973%2C%20a%20wrong%20precedent%20(galat%20parampara)%20started.%20In%201973%2C%20in%20the%20Kesavananda%20Bharati%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20gave%20the%20idea%20of%20basic%20structure%20saying%20Parliament%20can%20amend%20the%20Constitution%20but%20not%20its%20basic%20structure.%20With%20due%20respect%20to%20the%20judiciary%2C%20I%20cannot%20subscribe%20to%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691509680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F17tmiujk_dy-chandrachud-ani_625x300_18_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fonce-we-cease-to-be-judges-chief-justice-on-ranjan-gogois-remark-4280831%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20cease%20to%20be%20judges%2C%20whatever%20we%20say%20is%20just%20opinion%20and%20they%20are%20not%20binding%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20on%20Tue