ble%20about%20it.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20any%20central%20contract%20with%20the%20BCCI%2C%20we%20are%20not%20playing%20cricket%20in%20India%20anymore%20so%20it%20certainly%20does%20make%20you%20feel%20a%20little%20uncomfortable%20and%20unfair%20for%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20Uthappa%20replied%20to%20a%20PTI%20query%20during%20an%20interaction%20organised%20by%20Jio%20Cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20said%20that%2C%20the%20BCCI%20has%20certainly%20looked%20after%20all%20of%20us.%20I%20am%20certain%20whatever%20decision%20they%20take%20will%20be%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20the%20BCCI%20and%20the%20players%20who%20are%20going%20to%20play%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20certain%20solutions%20that%20can%20be%20reached.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20of%20communication%2C%20we%20could%20reach%20a%20solution%20that%20suits%20everybody.%E2%80%9D%20Uthappa%20said%20the%20approach%20of%20the%20team%20management%20and%20leadership%20would%20determine%20India's%20fortunes%20in%20the%20shortest%20format%2C%20as%20a%20new-look%20side%20under%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20auditioning%20with%20the%20next%20T20%20World%20Cup%20less%20than%20a%20year%20away.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20have%20a%20problem%20of%20plenty.%20There%20are%20enough%20people%20to%20represent%20the%20country%2C%20the%20quality%20is%20really%20high.%20Sometimes%20when%20you%20have%20high%20quality%20players%20you%20can%20have%20a%20headache%2C%20which%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20countries%20do%20not%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uthappa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20(about)%20how%20we%20decide%20to%20navigate%20through%20it%2C%20as%20a%20team%20management%20and%20what%20is%20the%20approach%20the%20team's%20leadership%20group%20has%2C%20will%20be%20critical%20to%20India's%20success%20in%20the%20co