ing%20company%2C%20Jindal%20Mine%2C%20who%20for%20years%20have%20been%20intruding%20with%20their%20plans%20to%20dig%20up%20iron%20ore%20in%20the%20lush%20hills%20that%20we%20have%20called%20home%20for%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20community%20members%20said%20in%20a%20petition%20signed%20by%20more%20than%206%2C700%20people.%20Jindal%20says%20a%20minority%20of%20residents%20oppose%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20obstacles%20faced%20by%20the%20company%20highlight%20the%20challenges%20of%20investing%20in%20South%20African%20mining%2C%20where%20decades%20of%20violations%20of%20environmental%20and%20social%20rights%20under%20apartheid%20eroded%20trust.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20chronic%20unemployment%20and%20poverty%20in%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20unequal%20nations%20often%20pits%20people%20against%20each%20other%20when%20projects%20offer%20the%20prospects%20of%20work%20and%20business%20opportunities%20for%20some.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Entembeni%20Crisis%20Forum%2C%20the%20group%20that%20organized%20the%20petition%2C%20said%20an%20assessment%20of%20the%20area%20that%20Jindal%20wants%20to%20mine%20shows%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20more%20than%203%2C000%20households%20and%203%2C000%20graves%20being%20moved.%20According%20to%20the%20firm%2C%20about%20350%20homes%20would%20be%20impacted%2C%20subject%20to%20a%20final%20determination%2C%20for%20the%20first%20stage%20of%20mining.%20That%20could%20take%20about%2015%20years%2C%20while%20the%20number%20of%20graves%20that%20would%20need%20to%20be%20relocated%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20assessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20resettlement%20decisions%20will%20be%20made%20in%20consultation%20with%20affected%20households%2C%26quot%3B%20Jindal%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20graves%20are%20to%20be%20exhumed%2C%20the%20exhumation%20of%20graves%20will%20follow%20the%20legal%20requirements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20forum%20said%20it's%20also%20concerned%20about%20the%20potential%20for%20environmental%20harm%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20agricultural%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mine%20lies%20about%2070%20kilometers%20(44%20miles)%20from%20the%20port%20of%20Richards%20Bay%20and%20the%20ore%2C%20which%20has%20a%20grade%20of%20about%2026%25%2C%20could%20be%20exported%20for%20use%20by%20Jindal's%20steel%20mills%20in%20Oman%20or%20India%20or%20sold%2C%20the%20company%20said.%20It%20expects%20to%20get%20a%20mining%20license%20next%20year%20and%20a%20processing%20plant%20will%20take%20two-and-a-half%20years%20to%20construct.%20It%20will%20be%20the%20second-biggest%20operation%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20South%20Africa%20after%20Kumba%20Iron%20Ore%20Ltd.'s%20Sishen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJindal%20also%20mines%20anthracite%20in%20South%20Africa%20and%20metallurgical%20coal%20in%20Mozambique.%20It%20signed%20a%20contract%20on%20July%2025%20to%20dig%20a%20coal%20mine%20and%20build%20power%20plants%20to%20supply%20Botswana%20with%20600%20megawatts%20of%20electricity.%20That%20project%20will%20start%20with%20construction%20of%20a%20300%20megawatt%20plant%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691506500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F7rd2ujag_map-1200_625x300_08_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgraves-a-barrier-for-jindal-steels-2-billion-south-african-iron-mine-4280764%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20plan%20by%20Jindal%20Steel%20%26amp%3B%20Power%20Ltd.%20to%20develop%20an%20up-to%20%242%20billion%20iron-ore%20mine%20in%20South%20Africa%20is%20facing%20opposition%20from%20communities%20who%20say%20the%20operation%20would%20require%20thousands%20of%20homes%20and%20graves%20to%20be%20relocated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgraves-a-barrier-for-jindal-steels-2-billion-south-african-iron-mine-4280764%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22