es%20Act%20(POCSO%20Act)%20was%20to%20protect%20children%20below%20the%20age%20of%2018%20from%20sexual%20exploitation%20and%20it%20was%20never%20meant%20to%20criminalise%20consensual%20romantic%20relationship%20between%20young%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20petitioner%2C%20currently%20around%2023%20years%20old%2C%20is%20already%20in%20custody%20since%20October%2015%2C%202021.%20Keeping%20the%20petitioner%20in%20jail%20will%20not%20serve%20any%20useful%20purpose.%20Rather%2C%20subjecting%20the%20young%20boy%20to%20the%20company%20of%20hardened%20criminals%20would%20do%20more%20harm%20than%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccordingly%2C%20the%20petitioner%20is%20admitted%20to%20regular%20bail%20subject%20to%20his%20furnishing%20personal%20bond%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%2F-%20and%20a%20Surety%20Bond%20in%20the%20like%20amount%20subject%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20the%20Trial%20Court%2FCMM%2FDuty%20Magistrate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20ordered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20present%20case%2C%20the%20FIR%20was%20registered%20at%20the%20instance%20of%20the%20girl%20who%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%2C%20her%20neighbour%2C%20had%20befriended%20her%20and%20established%20a%20physical%20relationship%20with%20her%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20marrying%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20said%20she%20subsequently%20discovered%20that%20she%20was%20pregnant%20and%20her%20medical%20examination%20revealed%20that%20it%20was%20too%20late%20for%20an%20abortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%2C%20the%20court%20recorded%20that%20the%20prosecutrix%20asserted%20in%20her%20statement%20that%20she%20never%20wanted%20to%20get%20a%20case%20registered%20against%20the%20petitioner%20but%20it%20seemed%20that%20the%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20by%20her%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20insistence%20of%20her%20family%20who%20were%20perhaps%20embarrassed%20after%20the%20discovery%20of%20prosecutrix's%20pregnancy%20which%20had%20surpassed%20the%20stage%20of%20its%20termination%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20court%20is%20cognizant%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20prosecutrix%20was%20a%20minor%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20it%20cannot%20be%20overlooked%20that%20the%20prosecutrix%20was%20aged%2017.5%20years%20and%20was%20thus%2C%20of%20sufficient%20maturity%20and%20intellectual%20capacity.%20The%20petitioner%20at%20the%20relevant%20time%20was%20aged%20about%2020%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20object%20of%20judicial%20custody%20is%20to%20secure%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20accused%20during%20the%20trial%20which%20can%20be%20ensured%20by%20putting%20in%20place%20appropriate%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20testimonies%20of%20the%20prosecutrix%20and%20her%20mother%20have%20already%20been%20recorded%2C%20therefore%2C%20there%20cannot%20be%20any%20apprehension%20about%20the%20material%20witnesses%20being%20influenced%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20asked%20the%20petitioner%20not%20to%20leave%20the%20city%20without%20permission%20and%20appear%20before%20the%20trial%20court%20whenever%20the%20case%20is%20taken%20up%20for%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20asked%20him%20to%20keep%20his%20mobile%20phone%20in%20working%20condition%20and%20not%20communicate%20with%20the%20witnesses%20or%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691502600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-05%2Flg1rco9_delhi-high-court-_625x300_18_May_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshe-had-sufficient-maturity-bail-to-man-jailed-over-relation-with-teen-4280126%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20granted%20bail%20to%20a%20man%20who