rnt%20about%20the%20community%20of%20pastoralists%2C%20camel%20herders%2C%20sheep%20goat%20rearers%2C%20and%20indigenous%20cow%20rearers.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20challenging%20geographies%20and%20extreme%20temperatures%2C%20these%20communities%20would%20travel%20eight%20months%20on%20foot%20covering%20800%20km%20of%20stretch%20with%20their%20herds%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPastoralism%20has%20been%20enriching%20the%20desert%20soil%20all%20these%20years.%20Whatever%20organic%20greenery%20that%20we%20see%20in%20deserts%20is%20because%20of%20their%20movement.%20When%20the%20pastoralists%20are%20on%20the%20move%20with%20livestock%2C%20their%20droppings%20rejuvenate%20the%20pasture%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20sells%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20camel%20milk%20ghee%2C%20biscuits%2C%20and%20Cheshire%20cheese%2C%20and%20cold-pressed%20oils.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fbahula-naturals-1-1691499258-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326698%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20sells%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20camel%20milk%20ghee%2C%20biscuits%2C%20and%20Cheshire%20cheese%2C%20and%20cold-pressed%20oils.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CCamels%20were%20also%20used%20to%20draw%20water%2C%20cultivate%20the%20farm%2C%20and%20for%20transportation%20purposes.%20But%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20man-made%20machinery%20and%20the%202015%20ban%2C%20these%20pastoralists%20started%20switching%20to%20daily%20wage%20jobs%20after%20leaving%20their%20camels%20on%20railway%20tracks%20to%20die%20as%20they%20could%20not%20earn%20a%20livelihood%20from%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20stable%20ways%20to%20make%20a%20living%20from%20animals%20and%20their%20products%2C%20these%20communities%20had%20to%20start%20working%20for%20daily%20wages%20in%20mines%20and%20brick%20kilns%20in%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20five%20years%20of%20research%2C%20Aakriti%20co-founded%20the%20Bikaner-based%20startup%20%E2%80%98Bahula%20Naturals%E2%80%99%20in%202022%2C%20along%20with%20Romal%20and%20Suraj%20Singh%20%E2%80%94%20who%20she%20met%20during%20the%20assignment.%20Together%2C%20they%20also%20work%20with%20local%20partners%20and%20non-profits%20such%20as%20Urmul%20Seemant%20Samiti%2C%20Desert%20Resource%20Centre%2C%20and%20Selco%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20the%20ship%20of%20the%20desert%20sail%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20is%20working%20to%20establish%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20net-zero%20dairy%20%E2%80%94%20wherein%20they%20collect%20milk%20from%204%2C000%20camel%2C%20sheep%2C%20and%20cow%20rearers%20in%20Bikaner%2C%20Jodhpur%2C%20Jaisalmer%2C%20and%20Nagaur%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20quality%20testing%2C%20the%20collected%20milk%20is%20stored%20in%20instant%20milk%20chillers%20that%20are%20claimed%20to%20bring%20the%20temperature%20down%20to%20four%20degrees%20within%20three%20m