0didn't%20expect%20to%20hear%20that%20at%20all.%20We%20thought%20we%20were%20going%20for%20another%20kind%20of%20treatment%20and%20it%20would%20work.%20It%20was%20like%20a%20gut%20punch.%20You%20never%20imagine%20them%20saying%20they%20can't%20do%20anything%20else%20for%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-razor-company-faces-boycott-calls-for-working-with-a-transgender-influencer-4280088%5C%22%3EUS%20Razor%20Company%20Faces%20Boycott%20Calls%20For%20Working%20With%20A%20Transgender%20Influencer%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20the%20sad%20news%2C%20Ms%20Alina%20and%20DJ's%20mother%20sprang%20into%20action%2C%20making%20plans%20for%20a%20mock%20%26quot%3Bwedding%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20had%20to%20happen%20super%20fast.%20We%20threw%20it%20together%20in%20less%20than%20two%20days%3B%20everything%20ended%20up%20being%20donated%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Alina%20said%20of%20the%20wedding%2C%20which%20was%20a%20garden%20ceremony%20with%20some%20100%20guests%20in%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20so%20precious%2C%20and%20it%20came%20together%20so%20well.%20Her%20dad%20gets%20to%20say%20he%20gave%20her%20away.%20A%20friend%20of%20ours%20officiated%2C%20a%20friend%20read%20a%20verse%20from%20the%20Bible%2C%20and%20her%20best%20friend%20was%20maid%20of%20honour%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Alina%20also%20praised%20her%20new%20son-in-law.%20%26quot%3BDJ%20is%20the%20sweetest%20soul%20you'll%20ever%20meet.%20He%20has%20a%20heart%20of%20gold%20and%20he%20really%20loves%20Emma%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Alina%20Edward%20revealed%20that%20Emma%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20healthy%20child%20until%20they%20took%20her%20to%20hospital%20because%20she%20fell%20over%20and%20medics%20discovered%20the%20cancer%20in%20the%20bones%20in%20her%20legs%20in%20April