d%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NCP%20chief%20has%20assured%20that%20he%20would%20be%20holding%20a%20rally%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20August%20in%20Pune%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20party%20workers%20and%20citizens%20on%20his%20political%20stand.%20He%20clarified%20to%20us%20that%20he%20will%20not%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jagtap%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawar%20Senior%20also%20reportedly%20told%20the%20visiting%20delegation%20that%20BJP%20is%20trying%20hard%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20party%20and%20its%20symbol%20are%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20faction%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar.%20However%2C%20he%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20assured%20them%20that%20he%20will%20not%20let%20the%20saffron%20party%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawar%E2%80%99s%20behaviour%20has%20lately%20created%20confusion%20not%20just%20among%20NCP%20workers%20but%20also%20among%20the%2026-party%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance.%20At%20an%20event%20held%20in%20Pune%20on%20August%201%2C%20the%20NCP%20patriarch%20shared%20the%20stage%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20The%20event%20was%20held%20to%20confer%20Modi%20with%20an%20award%20instituted%20in%20the%20honour%20of%20freedom%20fighter%20Lokmanya%20Bal%20Gangadhar%20Tilak.%20Despite%20INDIA%20parties%20objecting%20Pawar%20from%20sharing%20the%20stage%20with%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20at%20a%20time%20the%20opposition%20parties%20are%20forging%20an%20alliance%20and%20taking%20on%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20Pawar%20went%20ahead%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20event.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20event%20took%20place%20days%20after%20NCP%20was%20vertically%20split%20between%20Sharad%20and%20Ajit%20Pawars.%20The%20BJP%20took%20an%20active%20part%20in%20engineering%20the%20split%2C%20allege%20opposition%20parties%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20granted%20audience%20to%20his%20nephew%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20even%20after%20he%20walked%20away%20with%20nine