3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EBhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Ekta-Ugrahan)%2C%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20largest%20farmer%20organisation%2C%20marched%20towards%20the%20Governor%E2%80%99s%20House%20in%20Chandigarh.%20They%20submitted%20to%20the%20governor%20a%20letter%20demanding%20the%20immediate%20dismissal%20of%20the%20N.%20Biren%20Singh-led%20Manipur%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EThe%20protesters%20held%20top%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%20both%20at%20the%20centre%20and%20at%20the%20state%20responsible%20for%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%20They%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Econdemned%20the%20heinous%20crimes%20of%20parading%20women%20naked%20and%20inhuman%20acts%20of%20rape%20and%20murder.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20three-month-long%20mayhem%20has%20claimed%20over%20160%20lives%20and%20left%20several%20displaced.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EThey%20also%20sought%20strict%20action%20against%20those%20involved%20in%20these%20crimes%20in%20the%20strife-torn%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EThe%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-violence-cbi-to-probe-all-12-cases-of-crime-against-women-says-govt-101691399382308.html%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-violence-cbi-to-probe-all-12-cases-of-crime-against-women-says-govt-101691399382308.html%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1691565618711000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1wfJhJ5Fk1avPa8xw82RU0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECentre%20on%20Monday%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20will%20probe%2012%20FIRs%20relating%20to%20the%20crimes%20against%20women%20in%20violence-hit%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3ECalling%20the%20government%20action%20mere%20%E2%80%9Ceyewash%E2%80%9D%2C%20Harinder%20Bindu%2C%20women%20leader%20of%20BKU(Ekta-Ugrahan)%2C%20alleged%20that%20Manipur%20violence%20was%20part%20of%20a%20large%20conspiracy%20to%20divide%20ethnic%20communities%20in%20the%20state%20for%20vote%20polarisation%20just%20like%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08142307%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-13.37.54.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08142307%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-13.37.54.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08142307%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-13.37.54-300x175.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-667163%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22596%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPunjab%20farmers%20protest%20against%20Manipur%20violence%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Sunday%2C%20August%206%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20this%20is%20being%20done%20with%20greed%20for%20power%20and%20allowing%20crony%20corporates%20to%20take%20control%20of%20land%2C%20forest%2C%20and%20other%20natural%20resources%20by%20creating%20conflicts%20among%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EAnother%20woman%20leader%20Kuldeep%20Kaur%20Kussa%20said%20that%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20Hindus%20in%20Manipur%20targeted%20the%20minority%20Kuki%20tribal%20tribe%2C%20burning%20hundreds%20of%20their%20