2%3EHe%20demanded%20that%20all%20legal%2C%20administrative%2C%20and%20political%20steps%20must%20be%20immediately%20taken%20to%20restore%20the%20unity%20of%20Maitai%2C%20Kuki%2C%20and%20other%20ethnic%20communities%20of%20Manipur.%20Extensive%20confidence-building%20steps%20should%20be%20taken%20through%20people-to-people%20contact.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EHe%20also%20demanded%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20The%20Forest%20Conservation%20(Amendment)%20Act%202023%2C%20which%20he%20said%2C%20was%20passed%20to%20give%20undue%20benefits%20to%20crony%20capitalists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EUgrahan%2C%20whose%20organisation%20played%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20farm%20laws%20in%202021%2C%20says%20the%20Modi%20government%20first%20tried%20to%20destroy%20agriculture%20by%20bringing%20in%20three%20agricultural%20laws%2C%20and%20now%2C%20using%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Egovernment%20amended%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20so%20that%20natural%20resources%20of%20the%20northeastern%20states%20can%20be%20taken%20over.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20just%20farmers%20who%20protested%20the%20Manipur%20violence.%20Several%20other%20groups%20in%20Punjab%20have%20been%20accusing%20the%20Union%20government%20of%20acting%20with%20prejudice%20towards%20some%20communities.%20For%20instance%2C%20last%20week%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fpunjab%2Fprotests-over-violence-in-manipur-530168%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fpunjab%2Fprotests-over-violence-in-manipur-530168%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1691565618712000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1IBuvjGDh7CMOtPXI5--da%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseveral%20Christian%20organisations%3C%2Fa%3E