2F08%2Froti-rice-rate-august2023.pdf%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Crisil%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Etomatoes%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20retail%20markets%20has%20skyrocketed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fbusiness%2Ftomato-prices-ruling-up-to-rs-250-kg-centre-selling-at-rs-90-kg-in-delhi-ncr-patna-lucknow-news-303243%5C%22%3ERs%20250%20per%20kg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20it%20more%20expensive%20than%20petrol%20(Rs%2097%20per%20litre%20in%20Delhi).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Crisil%2C%20a%20vegetarian%20thali%20comprises%20roti%2C%20vegetables%20(onion%2C%20tomato%2C%20and%20potato)%2C%20rice%2C%20dal%2C%20curd%2C%20and%20salad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20non-vegetarian%20thali%2C%20chicken%20has%20been%20considered%20instead%20of%20dal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20take%20into%20account%20the%20retail%20price%20of%20a%20thali%2C%20which%20includes%20overhead%20costs%2C%20staff%20expenses%2C%20and%20profit%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20monthly%20change%20reflects%20the%20impact%20on%20the%20common%20man%E2%80%99s%20expenditure.%20The%20data%20also%20reveals%20the%20ingredients%20(cereals%2C%20pulses%2C%20broilers%2C%20vegetables%2C%20spices%2C%20edible%20oil%2C%20cooking%20gas)%20driving%20changes%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20thali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20noted%20that%20chili%20and%20cumin%20also%20became%20more%20expensive%2C%20their%20prices%20rising%2069%25%20and%2016%25%20on-month%2C%20respectively%2C%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20given%20the%20lower%20quantities%20of%20these%20ingredients%20used%20in%20a%20thali%2C%20their%20cost%20contribution%20remains%20lower%20than%20some%20of%20the%20vegetable%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ftomatoes-the-modi-government-has-made-a-pr-stunt-out-of-a-real-issue%5C%22%3ETomatoes%3A%20The%20Modi%20Government%20Has%20Made%20a%20PR%20Stunt%20Out%20of%20a%20Real%20Issue%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20a%20non-vegetarian%20thali%20rose%20at%20a%20slower%20pace%20as%20the%20price%20of%20broilers%2C%20comprising%20more%20than%2050%25%20of%20the%20cost%2C%20likely%20declined%203-5%25%20on-month%20in%20July%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20vegetarian%20thali%20was%20Rs%2033.7%20and%20that%20of%20a%20non-vegetarian%20thali%20was%20Rs%2066.8.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20one%20could%20pay%20Rs%2026.3%20for%20a%20vegetarian%20thali%20and%20Rs%2060%20for%20non-vegetarian%20thali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20previous%20months%2C%20a%20vegetarian%20thali%20was%20priced%20around%20Rs%2025%2C%20and%20a%20non-vegetarian%20thali%20around%20Rs%2059.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fahmedabad%2Frestaurants-shelling-out-50-more-for-vegetables-spices%2Farticleshow%2F102408487.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20restaurants%20are%20shelling%20out%2050%25%20more%20for%20spices%20and%20vegetables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mid-sized%20restaurant%20usually%20spends%20around%201.5-2%20lakh%20a%20month%20on%20vegetables%2C%20the%20daily%20said%2C%20citing%20a%20restaurant%20owner.%20However%2C%20in%20July%2C%20these%20costs%20went%20as%20high%20as%202.5-3%20lakh%2C%20due%20to%20the%20soaring%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691481608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08123907%2Fimage-1198.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffood%2Ftomato-prices-monthly-cost-of-vegetarian-thali-rises-by-34-crisil%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20price%20of%20tomato%20rose%20by%20233%25%20month-on-month%20to%20Rs%20110%2Fkg%20in%20July%20from%20Rs%2033%2Fkg%20in%20June.%20In%20retail%20markets%2C%20it%20has%20skyrocketed%20to%20Rs%20250%20pe