3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20we%20have%20Gowdang%20Rani%20%E2%80%94%20the%20full%20moon%20queen%20who%20holds%20a%20lot%20of%20importance%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Bodo%20community.%20Whenever%20there%20is%20a%20war%20or%20some%20sad%20occasion%2C%20she%20is%20believed%20to%20visit%20her%20people%20to%20motivate%20them.%20Then%20there%20is%20Gambari%20Sikla%2C%20who%20made%20historical%20contributions%2C%20such%20as%20fighting%20against%20both%20the%20Bhutanese%20and%20British%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20toys%20look%20like%20us%20and%20are%20dressed%20in%20traditional%20clothes%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F95506%2Fhironmoy-gogoi-assamese-ethnic-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauthentic%20Assamese%20%3C%2Fa%3Esaree%2C%20along%20with%20traditional%20accessories%2C%20swords%20etc.%20The%20attire%20can%20be%20changed.%20All%20the%20toys%20are%20handmade%20and%20plastic%20free.%20We%20also%20make%20soft%20toys%20of%20animals%20such%20as%20wild%20buffalo%20and%20fish%2C%20as%20they%20have%20a%20great%20significance%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHandmade%2C%20plastic-free%20toys%20that%20tell%20stories%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirat%20says%20that%20all%20the%20materials%20used%20to%20create%20these%20toys%20are%20sourced%20from%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302408%2Fhistory-of-ima-keithal-largest-all-women-market-imphal-manipur-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20local%20markets.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20local%20economy%20needs%20a%20good%20boost%3B%20my%20community%E2%80%99s%20youth%20do%20not%20have%20many%20opportunities.%20They%20either%20leave%20the%20village%20and%20move%20to%20cities%20or%20join%20the%20Army.%20I%20try%20to%20employ%20as%20many%20artisans%20from%20the%20community%20itself%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20a%20work%20opportunity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20they%20have%20sold%20around%20100%20toys%20so%20far.%20Each%20toy%20is%20usually%20priced%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%20800%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20depending%20on%20the%20work%20involved.%20They%20are%20also%20working%20on%20adding%20more%20categories.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20receive%20our%20toys%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-3-1690981932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kirat%20hires%20people%20from%20his%20community%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20work%20opportunities%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-3-1690981932.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-3-1690981932-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-3-1690981932-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-3-1690981932-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-3-1690981932-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326117%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKirat%20hires%20the%20artisans%20from%20his%20community%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20work%20opportunities%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Zankla%20Studio%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20shares%20that%20the%20real%20test%20of%20the%20toys%20came%20when%20he%20received%20an%20order%20from%20a%