0quantity%2C%20for%20which%20I%20would%20get%20Rs%2050%2C%20now%20I%20earn%20Rs%20350%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Nitin%2C%20who%20grows%20tomatoes%2C%20grapes%2C%20and%20onions%20on%20a%20five-acre%20land%20in%20his%20village%20Matur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-3-1690551720.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20least%2050%2C000%20farmers%20across%20the%20country%20have%20been%20able%20to%20reap%20benefits%20from%20excess%20produce.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-3-1690551720.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-3-1690551720-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-3-1690551720-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-3-1690551720-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fraheja-solar-3-1690551720-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325726%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20least%2050%2C000%20farmers%20across%20the%20country%20have%20been%20able%20to%20reap%20benefits%20from%20excess%20produce.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20five%20months%2C%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20earn%20an%20additional%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20by%20selling%20excess%20produce%20that%20would%20otherwise%20go%20to%20waste.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20many%20farmers%20questioned%20me%20on%20why%20was%20I%20investing%20in%20a%20solar%20dryer%20and%20what%20benefit%20it%20could%20bring%20me.%20They%20also%20mocked%20me%20saying%20it%20would%20not%20be%20a%20