ity-un-sdg-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematernal%20mortality%20%3C%2Fa%3Erate%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20claims%20that%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20reduce%20maternal%20mortality%20by%2010%20percent%20in%20the%20regions%20he%20has%20worked.%20For%20him%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20work%20is%20extremely%20satisfying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20five%20years%20into%20any%20corporate%20job%2C%20the%20work%20is%20pretty%20much%20the%20same.%20I%20chose%20entrepreneurship%20because%20it%20gives%20me%20more%20learning%20opportunities.%20Instead%20of%20working%20in%20a%20big%20Fortune%20500%20company%2C%20this%20work%20gives%20me%20immense%20gratification.%20It%20is%20fulfilling%20to%20see%20we%20are%20able%20to%20save%20lives%20with%20our%20devices%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20shares%20that%20he%20now%20intends%20to%20expand%20their%20services%20in%20North%20and%20Northeast%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Frchiips.org%2Fnfhs%2FNFHS-5_FCTS%2FIndia.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20%E2%80%93%205%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20by%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare.%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FFeaturesDeatils.aspx%3FNoteId%3D151238%26ModuleId%2520%3D%25202%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESignificant%20Decline%20in%20Maternal%20Mortality%20in%20India%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20by%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20on%2014%20December%202022.%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Senthil%20Kumar%3C%2Fem%3